{"tid":2167340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登指若當選會令疫情受控　做屬於「美國人的總統」","createTime":"2020-08-21T05:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T08:07:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"98c0b1b27561d2637cb564d1149007b4650cb5a9","tid":2167340,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:02:14.000Z","msg":"美國前副總統拜登正式成為民主黨總統候選人。他在演說時批評總統特朗普為美國帶來太多帶來黑暗、分裂，指自己雖然是民主黨人，但如果當選將會不分黨派做一個「美國人的總統」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登批評特朗普應對新型肺炎疫情不力，自己當選後會令國內疫情受控，包括研發提供即時檢測結果的病毒快速測試、為民眾提供足夠醫療及保護裝備等。拜登又批評特朗普領導下，美國經濟下滑、企業倒閉、失業率高企，認為如果特朗普連任，美國的後果將不可設想。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545059-20200821.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545059-20200821.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=e9095138\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545059-20200821.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=915368cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545059-20200821.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9ca2150ad2a1cdf0d0cc5d6b122a845b84c9ccc4","tid":2167340,"uid":286897,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bded3c39c6a8edf837be743ea68599546382d82b","tid":2167340,"uid":61032,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"全部人唔驗咪受控囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329d47bc8e476cfa57dedc64e42309750d890d77","tid":2167340,"uid":31151,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:20:17.000Z","msg":"拜登又批評特朗普領導下，美國經濟下滑、企業倒閉、失業率高企<br />\n<br />\n平行時空？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c657ec7e1e8a578da399c63ba9df5ac197a79540","